            <p>NutriAI Advisor is an innovative mobile app that transforms how you manage your diet. Using advanced AI, it analyzes your food intake and health conditions to deliver personalized nutrition plans. Whether you're managing diabetes, hypertension, or aiming for a balanced lifestyle, NutriAI Advisor supports your journey with tailored recommendations and smart reminders. Designed for everyone from fitness enthusiasts to those with specific health needs, it makes healthy eating simple and effective.</p>
