        <section id="how-it-works">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> How It Works</h2>
            <p>NutriAI Advisor guides you to better health in five easy steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Set Up Your Profile</strong>: Input your age, gender, activity level, and health conditions to create a personalized nutrition plan.</li>
                <li><strong>Log Your Food</strong>: Record meals using text, voice, or images for accurate tracking.</li>
                <li><strong>Analyze Your Intake</strong>: View detailed nutrition breakdowns and compare them to your daily goals.</li>
                <li><strong>Receive Recommendations</strong>: Get AI-driven food suggestions tailored to your dietary and health needs.</li>
                <li><strong>Follow Smart Reminders</strong>: Stay consistent with notifications for meals, water, and exercise.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>
